{"tid":2303952,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"買iPad 8/Air/Pro定MacBook定Surface好？","createTime":"2020-11-28T10:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T06:05:46.000Z","uid":43987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ae128807627e9f5b4b02ff873f15cadd4bfca4ea","tid":2303952,"uid":43987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"小弟有一部desktop平時做晒文書野同打機用<br />\n基本上係屋企做電腦野係冇問題<br />\n最近想入手一部輕身啲既機 主要係可以上堂用黎睇下slide 或者係出面做普通文書野 同埋屋企睇下片打下機咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果想用到3-4年既話想問iPad8夠唔夠做？定係要upgrade去air/pro？<br />\n<br />\n我見網上面講a12z同a14好似差唔多咁，同埋想知iPadOS做文書野方唔方便？如果唔方便可能會考慮埋MacBook/surface<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感謝各位解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71676d880863366847637a7c0c95ae361140ce50","tid":2303952,"uid":299311,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:59:24.000Z","msg":"Ipad做文書嘢會好痛苦<br />\nJot notes反而一流"},{"pid":"f7e233520e71a882f0b3f428a8ba50425624417d","tid":2303952,"uid":152432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T11:03:41.000Z","msg":"MacBook Air完勝<br />\n個價錢 電池同重量<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fee24b28e7ca4cee38d7e6397eb5d9575b738ba","tid":2303952,"uid":43987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71676d880863366847637a7c0c95ae361140ce50","tid":2303952,"uid":299311,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:59:24.000Z","msg":"Ipad做文書嘢會好痛苦<br />\nJot notes反而一流"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"其實都真係好少要係出面做文書野 都係最多用黎上堂/傾下project"},{"pid":"ce701e84d6962283ef4c76ac976f2bed9f4a144b","tid":2303952,"uid":43987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f7e233520e71a882f0b3f428a8ba50425624417d","tid":2303952,"uid":152432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T11:03:41.000Z","msg":"MacBook Air完勝<br /